---
title: Sweet Pepper, Chorizo and Black Bean Taquitos with Monterey Jack Cheese and Fresh Salsa
description: Nutritious and delicious black beans take centre stage in this fun veggie recipe. Cooked with chorizo, sweet onions, peppers and zesty chipotle sauce, everything is then wrapped and baked with stretchy Monterey Jack cheese for ultimate cheese pull satisfaction!

